### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Login first to get token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Get all stores with pagination (default: page=1, limit=10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJhZG1pbiIsInJvbGUiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc1NTE1MzQ2NCwiZXhwIjoxNzU1MjM5ODY0fQ.LyMu2IFUtFmvrXN97I0NUJjCN1SjwRygl0oAUsVy8Kc

### Get all stores with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6MSwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJhZG1pbiIsInJvbGUiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTc1NTE1MzQ2NCwiZXhwIjoxNzU1MjM5ODY0fQ.LyMu2IFUtFmvrXN97I0NUJjCN1SjwRygl0oAUsVy8Kc

### Get all stores with search filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores?search=toko&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all stores with region filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores?region=Jakarta&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all stores with status filter (active stores only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores?status=active&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get stores by branch code with pagination (default: page=1, limit=10, onlyInduk=true)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get stores by branch code with custom pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?page=2&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get stores by branch code with search filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?search=induk&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get stores by branch code including non-induk stores
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?onlyInduk=false&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get stores by branch code with status filter (active stores only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?status=active&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get stores by branch code with multiple filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?page=1&limit=5&search=toko&onlyInduk=true&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get store by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create new store (Admin/Manager only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "storeCode": "T001",
  "storeName": "Toko Contoh",
  "branch": "001",
  "cab": "001",
  "notes": "INDUK",
  "region": "Jakarta",
  "city": "Jakarta Pusat",
  "address": "Jl. Contoh No. 123",
  "dbHost": "localhost",
  "dbUser": "user",
  "dbPassword": "password",
  "dbName": "database_name",
  "isActive": true
}

### Update store (Admin/Manager only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "storeName": "Toko Contoh Updated",
  "address": "Jl. Contoh Updated No. 456",
  "isActive": true
}

### Delete store (Admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test database connection
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/test-connection
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "host": "localhost",
  "username": "user",
  "password": "password",
  "database": "database_name"
}

### ===== PAGINATION EXAMPLES =====

### Example: Get first page (page 1) with 10 items per page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example: Get second page (page 2) with 10 items per page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?page=2&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Example: Get third page (page 3) with 5 items per page
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stores/branch/001?page=3&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===== RESPONSE FORMAT EXPLANATION =====
# The response will include:
# {
#   "stores": [...],           // Array of store objects
#   "totalItems": 25,          // Total number of stores matching criteria
#   "totalPages": 3,           // Total number of pages (totalItems / limit)
#   "currentPage": 1,          // Current page number
#   "branchCode": "001"        // Branch code used for filtering
# }
#
# To navigate pages:
# - Use 'page' parameter to specify which page you want
# - Use 'limit' parameter to specify how many items per page
# - Check 'totalPages' to know the maximum page number available
# - Use 'totalItems' to know total records matching your criteria